Perfect! Now I have all the information I need. Let me compile a comprehensive report of all the UI patterns, theming, and animation conventions used in the iskrib_v3 codebase.

## Comprehensive UI Pattern Analysis for iskrib_v3 Paragraph Commenting Feature

I've thoroughly explored the iskrib_v3 codebase. Here's a detailed breakdown of the design conventions and patterns for the paragraph commenting feature:

---

### 1. GLOBAL THEME & CSS VARIABLES

**File:** `C:\Users\johnm\iskrib_v3\client\src\index.css`

#### Light Mode (`:root`)
- **Backgrounds:**
  - `--bg-primary: #FAF9F6` (main background)
  - `--bg-secondary: #F3F1ED` (secondary surfaces)
  - `--bg-elevated: #FFFFFF` (cards, modals)
  - `--bg-overlay: rgba(250,249,246,0.3)` (semi-transparent overlay)
  - `--bg-glass: rgba(255,255,255,0.55)` (glass morphism)
  - `--bg-glass-border: rgba(200,180,150,0.2)` (glass morphism borders)
  - `--bg-pill: rgba(120,100,80,0.06)` (subtle background)

- **Text Colors:**
  - `--text-primary: #1A1612` (main text)
  - `--text-heading: #12100D` (headings)
  - `--text-secondary: #6B6560` (secondary text)
  - `--text-body: #8A8480` (body text)
  - `--text-muted: #A8A29E` (muted)
  - `--text-faint: #C0BBB5` (very faint)

- **Borders & Shadows:**
  - `--border-light: rgba(120,100,80,0.12)`
  - `--border-card: rgba(120,100,80,0.08)`
  - `--shadow-card: 0 1px 4px rgba(80,60,40,0.06), 0 4px 16px rgba(80,60,40,0.04)`
  - `--shadow-modal: 0 8px 32px rgba(80,60,40,0.12)`

- **Accent Colors:**
  - `--accent-purple: #C4943E` (primary accent, golden)
  - `--accent-amber: #D4A853` (accent variant)
  - `--accent-sage: #8A9E7A` (alternative accent)

#### Dark Mode (`[data-theme="dark"]`)
- **Backgrounds:**
  - `--bg-primary: #0C0C0C`
  - `--bg-secondary: #141414`
  - `--bg-elevated: #1A1A18`
  - `--bg-overlay: rgba(0,0,0,0.4)`
  - `--bg-glass: rgba(255,255,255,0.05)`
  - `--bg-glass-border: rgba(255,240,210,0.08)`

- **Text Colors:**
  - `--text-primary: #F0EBE3`
  - `--text-heading: #F5F0E8`
  - `--text-secondary: #B0A89E`
  - `--text-body: #908880`
  - `--text-muted: #6B6560`

- **Shadows:**
  - `--shadow-card: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.3)`
  - `--shadow-modal: 0 8px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.5)`

- **Accent Colors:**
  - `--accent-purple: #D4A853` (lighter in dark mode)
  - `--accent-amber: #E0BA6A`

---

### 2. EXISTING COMMENT SYSTEM ARCHITECTURE

**Components:**
- `C:\Users\johnm\iskrib_v3\client\src\components\comments\comments.jsx` - Main comment section (slide-up modal)
- `C:\Users\johnm\iskrib_v3\client\src\components\comments\commentsCards.jsx` - Individual comment cards with nesting
- `C:\Users\johnm\iskrib_v3\client\src\components\comments\comments.css` - Styling

#### Comments Panel Structure
```
.cm-parent-container
├─ .cm-header (title + close btn)
├─ .cm-list (scrollable comment cards)
│  └─ .cm-card (repeating comment)
│     ├─ .cm-thread-line (nested indicator)
│     └─ .cm-card-content
│        ├─ .cm-user-row (avatar, name, badge, date)
│        ├─ .cm-body (comment text)
│        ├─ .cm-card-actions (reply/toggle buttons)
│        └─ .cm-reply-input-wrapper (collapsible reply input)
└─ .cm-input-area (textarea + submit)
```

#### Key Comment Card Styling Patterns
- **Avatar:** 22px circles with optional legend/og badge rings
- **Spacing:** Uses gap-based layouts, consistent 0.5rem/0.75rem padding
- **Borders:** `var(--border-card)` for subtle dividers
- **Buttons:** Rounded (border-radius: 20px for pill-style)
- **Reply nesting:** Indentation with `margin-left: 20px` and thread lines
- **Character count:** Shows "X/200" with red highlight when near limit
- **Fonts:** 
  - UI elements: `var(--font-ui)` ("Outfit", sans-serif)
  - Comment body: `var(--font-serif)` ("Lora", serif)

#### Animation Patterns (from comments.jsx)
```javascript
// Slide-up entrance
initial={{y: '100vh', opacity: 0}}
animate={{
    y: 0,
    opacity: 1,
    transition: {type: 'spring', damping: 25, stiffness: 200}
}}
exit={{y: '-100vh', opacity: 0, transition: {duration: 0.2}}}

// Reply input expand/collapse
initial={{ height: 0, opacity: 0 }}
animate={{ height: "auto", opacity: 1 }}
exit={{ height: 0, opacity: 0 }}
transition={{ duration: 0.2 }}
```

---

### 3. LEXICAL EDITOR THEMING & PARAGRAPH RENDERING

**File:** `C:\Users\johnm\iskrib_v3\client\src\components\HomePage\Editor\editor.css`

